        <title>Microtones in Auxy</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[akabillposters]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p><a href="https://disco.auxy.co/t/post-your-great-auxy-feature-idea-here/1129/215">I asked about it a while back</a> (<a href="https://disco.auxy.co/t/how-automation-works/1086/46">a couple of times</a>), but no real, conclusive response.</p>
<p>I love me some detune and it would help thicken things up…<br>
…<em>and</em>, with a bit of automation, we’d be able to create ‘drunk/wonky’ notes/chords. think Boards of Canada or Lorn.</p>
<p>And I’d certainly be interested to hear what someone who made microtonal music would do with Auxy.</p>
