        <title>Microtones in Auxy</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[wagneric]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Pitch automation snaps to half-tones, unfortunately, but I find that if you do, for example, a half-step over a long duration (8 bars), and experiment a bit, you can come close to what you want.  It’s pretty fun to try to write a melody while the pitch is sliding.</p>
